---
title: User Registration
description: New user signup flow with email verification
---
sequenceDiagram
    %% @desc User: New user signing up for an account
    %% @desc AuthService: Handles registration, password hashing and verification
    %% @desc UserDB: Stores user credentials and profiles
    %% @desc EmailService: Sends transactional emails (verification, notifications)
    actor User
    participant AuthService as Auth Service
    participant UserDB as User Database
    participant EmailService as Email Service

    User->>AuthService: POST /register (name, email, password)
    AuthService->>UserDB: SELECT user WHERE email = ?
    UserDB-->>AuthService: No record found
    AuthService->>AuthService: Hash password with bcrypt
    AuthService->>UserDB: INSERT user (name, email, hash, verified=false)
    UserDB-->>AuthService: User created (id)
    AuthService->>EmailService: sendVerificationEmail(email, token)
    EmailService-->>AuthService: Queued
    AuthService-->>User: 201 Created (check your email)

    User->>AuthService: GET /verify?token=abc123
    AuthService->>UserDB: UPDATE user SET verified=true WHERE token=?
    UserDB-->>AuthService: Updated
    AuthService-->>User: 200 OK (account active)
